ProtoResult:
. "The series $\sum_{n=k}^\infty f_ng_n$ converges uniformly 
   on $S$ if $$ f_{n+1}(x)\le f_n(x),\quad x\in S,\quad n\ge k,
   $$ $\{f_n\}$ converges uniformly to zero on $S$ and $$ 
   \|g_k+g_{k+1}+\cdots+g_n\|_S\le M,\quad n\ge k, $$ for some 
   constant $M$"
